      personal information in exchange for a reward or share our link with your
      friends or colleagues and receive rewards when they sign up to use our
      Services. (The referred party may also receive rewards for signing up via
      your referral.) These programs are entirely voluntary and allow us to grow
      our business and provide additional benefits to you. The value of your
      data to us depends on how you ultimately use our Services, whereas the
      value of the referred party’s data to us depends on whether the referred
      party ultimately becomes a User and uses our Services. Said value will be
      reflected in the incentive offered in connection with each program.
